{"tid":2416900,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[TSLA] 教主：法定貨幣負利率   「只有『傻瓜』才不理Bitcoin」","createTime":"2021-02-21T12:10:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T15:29:00.000Z","uid":51620,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0551139c5b6fe9894b3198e0a7a654b9c03c35ae","tid":2416900,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:10:26.000Z","msg":"特斯拉（Tesla）執行長馬斯克（Elon Musk）近日不斷表態支持比特幣等加密貨幣，Tesla 更宣佈已持有價值 15 億美元的比特幣（Bitcoin）。最近馬斯克繼續在 Twitter 發表其對買入比特幣的看法，他認為在流動性方面，持有比特幣也算是冒險行為，但當法定貨幣的實際利率為負時，只有「傻瓜」才不會分散投資。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/22-1-1280x853.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F22-1-1280x853.jpg&h=a23238e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全球最大加密或幣交易所之一的幣安 ( Binance ) CEO 趙長鵬在受訪時表示，儘管馬斯克對狗狗幣如此青睞有加，但讓其心甘情願砸下 15 億美元重金的，終究還是比特幣。馬斯克就此在 Twitter 上解釋：「Tesla 的舉動並非直接反映我的意見，持有一些比特幣，對一間被納入標普 500 指數的公司而言，算是冒險行為；但在流動性方面，持有比特幣比持有現金稍微沒那麼蠢。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2021/02/20/elonmuskbitcoin/fun-tech/?fbclid=IwAR2mbKRG2KtpXRGZP4rpIktyMYB8IpxwKDS11KScGyJBbm09DfEWDm0S-uE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2021%2F02%2F20%2Felonmuskbitcoin%2Ffun-tech%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2mbKRG2KtpXRGZP4rpIktyMYB8IpxwKDS11KScGyJBbm09DfEWDm0S-uE&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnb32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=5029f7d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2021/02/20/elonmuskbitcoin/fun-tech/?fbclid=IwAR2mbKRG2KtpXRGZP4rpIktyMYB8IpxwKDS11KScGyJBbm09DfEWDm0S-uE</a>"},{"pid":"21e735a6c21c42b0677cf7c5f44aea04f8100789","tid":2416900,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c37e480f7593a2002b8d5254ce4eccdbbaf7869d","tid":2416900,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:13:09.000Z","msg":"儘管馬斯克對狗狗幣如此青睞有加，但讓其心甘情願砸下 15 